      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but calling it life-threatening seems kinda extreme for a plant, right? i've heard from a few friends that a little bit of it is fine. if i just lower my dose of zoloft over a week or two while starting the st johns wort, how much of the herb would be safe to take to make sure i don't feel the withdrawal? just looking for a rough idea so i can feel better sooner.",
